<T>__{hard cut to:}
<L>__{exterior venice, grand canal day}
<A>__{a beauty shot of the grand canal: magnificent palaces and churches soar upwards on either side in all their glory. push in on a launch labelled danieli, travelling fast over the water. cara shakes her head to let the wind ruffle her hair. camera continues past her to reveal frank, clutching the railing beside her, afraid to wake up.}
<L>__{interior danieli hotel, entrance hall day}
<A>__{frank leads us through the distinctive, revolving glass door into the low ceilinged entrance lobby. discover cara at the desk talking to the receptionist.}
