<D>__{you have a booking in the name of mason.}
<C>__{receptionist}
<D>__{si, signorina.}
<C>__{cara}
<D>__{signora. that's my husband.}
<A>__{she nods at frank. for a second, the receptionist cannot keep the surprise out of his eyes. this glamorous, superbly dressed creature is married to a dull, american tourist in a t shirt? he recovers his composure and alters his manner at once.}
<C>__{receptionist}
<D>__{very good, senora mason. welcome to the danieli. you are in the doge's our premiere suite.}
